name: Blaze Maw Freezer Behemoth
text: The Inferno Maw Chiller's legend grew till it morphed, becoming the Frostflame Leviathan Cabinet. It towered in the silent glade, its aura of power visible in swirling frost and flame. Those who remembered whispered of its ancestor, Inferno Maw, now pale in comparison to this majestic, fearsome entity.

data.revised_prompt: An evolved chilling device known as the Cataclysmic Blaze Freezer stands tall with a strengthened frame made of obsidian. Upon opening its door, it reveals an endless, frost-shrouded void from within. Out of its gaping maw, striking blue flames burst forth, radiating a white-hot intensity. This frost-bound, ominous device now produces a roar so powerful and thunderous that it reverberates across different dimensions. Now it is guarded by creatures of ice and fire elemental nature that hover around it, as if ensnared by its captivating power.
